    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-5" id="accordion-1-content-5" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Adobe Substance 3D lets you create product imagery and digital twins for use across social media, ecommerce, advertising campaigns, and more. Swap variants, change perspectives, and place products in any scene to produce accurate, photorealistic visuals at scale. Learn more about <a href="/creativecloud/plans/?plan=individual&amp;filter=3dar" daa-ll="Substance 3D for med-8--How can Adobe Substa">Substance 3D for medium and large businesses.</a></div></div></div></div>
